"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.6.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.6.4</span> 標題：樓上的房間、樓房、屋頂的房間（upper room, roof chamber）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עֲלִיָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘aliyah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:20\">JDG 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:23\">JDG 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:24\">JDG 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:25\">JDG 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:1\">2SA 19:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19\">1KI 17:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:23\">1KI 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:2\">2KI 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:11\">2KI 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:12\">2KI 23:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:11\">1CH 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:9\">2CH 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31\">NEH 3:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:32\">NEH 3:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:3\">PSA 104:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13\">PSA 104:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:14\">JER 22:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">蘭：עִלִּי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘ili)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:11\">DAN 6:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַעֲלָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma‘alah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:6\">AMO 9:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἀνάγαιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： anagaion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:15\">MRK 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:12\">LUK 22:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ὑπερῷον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： huperōion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:13\">ACT 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:37\">ACT 9:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:39\">ACT 9:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:8\">ACT 20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob3:10\">TOB 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob3:17\">TOB 3:17</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0032_house_upperroom.png\" alt=\"帶上層房間的房子\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">帶上層房間的房子 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>樓上的房間是指在底層（地面層）上面一層的房間（該層在美式英語中為第二層，在其他大多數語言中為第一層）。樓上房間通常不會占整個樓層的面積，而是只占屋頂的一部分。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:20\">JDG 3:20</a> 中，希伯來文短語<em>‘aliyath mqerah</em> （在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:24\">JDG 3:24</a> 中也叫做<em>cheder mqerah</em> ）指專門為乘涼而建造的一間樓房。由於位置比較高，所以風相對較大，而且可能是朝北的，因此受到的日曬較少。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:6\">1KI 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:8\">1KI 6:8</a> 提到圍繞聖殿外側建造的二樓和三樓（美式英語）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:8\">1KI 6:8</a> 指的是「中間層的入口」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 直譯）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Hebrew Old Testament Text Project (UBS)\">HOTTP</abbr> 對此提出以下註解：「這些樓層可能是|u開放式|u*的拱廊或走廊。因此，經文可以不必提到開放式的地面層的入口，但有必要提到第一（或中間）和第二（或最高）層的入口。」這個註解是根據希伯來文本得出的結論，因為經文清楚提到中間層有入口，並且有樓梯通向中間層，又從中間層上到頂層。然而，《七十士譯本》和一個古老的猶太亞蘭文譯本（《他爾根》）都認為，在第8節末尾出現了兩次的希伯來文形容詞<em>tikonah</em> （「中間」）都是指中間層；但是，第一次其實是指最下面一層。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 贊同這個意見，英文意為：「通往最下層的入口是在殿的右邊轉角；通過一條螺旋樓梯上到中間層，再從中間層上到第三層。」</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:3\">PSA 104:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:13\">PSA 104:13</a> ：希伯來文<em>‘aliyoth</em> 在這些經文中指上帝的居所。許多譯本都沒有按字面翻譯。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 在兩處都譯為“home”（「家」），而<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在第3節譯為“home”（「家」），在第13節譯為“the sky”（「天」）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 分別譯為“palace”（「宮殿」）和“halls”（「大廳」）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
